adviseScripts.text: Subordinate,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I still can't believe I'm actually out at sea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Am I dreaming?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Pinch Helm's cheek.
Hold Helm's hand.
Ow!
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I guess that proves it's not a dream.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: But you didn't have to pinch so hard...
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It kind of hurts.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Your hand is so warm.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Since I can feel that warmth so clearly, I know for sure that I'm not dreaming.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I quietly gaze at the ocean.
Do you have a robe or anything I can wear?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Preferably one that reaches the ankles.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Can't say I do.
Let me see...
Are you sure?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Then can I have a look? Just in case there's one lying around.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Thanks.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Even though I'm already wearing a jacket,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: it still feels awkward being in this swimsuit.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I help Helm look for something she can wear over her swimsuit.
Subordinate.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: If you see someone drowning,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: what is the first thing you should do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Tell you.
Jump into the water.
Correct.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'm the best swimmer out of all of us,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: so if you ever see someone having trouble staying above water, tell me right away.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Wrong answer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You wouldn't be able to bring Nikkes back ashore,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: so if you do ever see someone drowning, tell me straight away.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm tells me more swimming safety rules.
Helm stares at the beach as if in a reverie.
What are you thinking?
... Oh, nothing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'm sorry for thinking about other things while I'm with you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Oh, I didn't see you there. Sorry, I was thinking about something.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It's fine, don't worry about me.
... Thank you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I have a meaningful session with Helm.
The breeze at night is so refreshing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It'd be a shame to spend the entire night here.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Should we take an evening stroll?
Want a beer?
Good idea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I can't wait!
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Subordinate,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: you should know the adverse health effects of consuming alcohol.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: ... Besides, I can't drink.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: How about going on a walk instead?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I take a nice nighttime stroll along the beach.
I feel like swimsuits don't really suit me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: What do you think?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You look good now.
Your uniform suits you better.
Thank you,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: but no matter what I do, I feel awkward in them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Huh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You think so too?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I just feel like I look so silly in this.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I want to change back into my usual clothes as soon as possible.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I talk with Helm about clothes.
It's kind of spooky at night.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It feels like a ghost could pop up at any minute.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: ... So. You think I'm human, huh?
Don't be afraid, I'll protect you.
Pfft...!
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It's funny seeing you say this with that face, Subordinate.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for giving me a good laugh. I don't feel so scared anymore.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: No,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I should be the one protecting you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: *Swish swish swish*
Eeeek!
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm leans over and grabs me tightly.
I think there's something behind us!
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I comfort Helm throughout our session.
Isn't the Admire splendid?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It's so massive and majestic... just looking at it excites me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You look like you were meant to be on it.
I agree.
You really know how to make a person feel great.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Thank you for saying that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Looks like I'm not the only one who feels that way.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'm sure everyone thinks the same thing when they lay eyes on the Admire.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I talk about the Admire.
Check out this tiny fish.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Isn't it adorable?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: ... Blech.
Looks a lot like you.
You don't like fish?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'm sorry. I didn't know.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Actually, I'm not a huge fan either.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I just figured it was appropriate to show you this since we're at the beach.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Like me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Sure. Because it's adorable.
I take it that's supposed to be a compliment?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Yeah. All right. Thanks.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I talk with Helm about fish.
I'm craving some fresh fruit today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: What's your favorite fruit, Subordinate?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: If we're talking about summertime, watermelons.
If we're talking about summertime, peaches.
So you also like watermelons.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: A lot of people seem to like watermelons,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: but I prefer peaches.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You like peaches, too?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You're just like me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It doesn't matter whether they're crunchy or soft, I just love them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Although I don't get too many chances to try them out.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I converse about our favorite fruits.
Anis and Mary have both been pestering me,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: telling me to rest,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: but I've been resting this entire time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I don't know what they're getting at when they say 'rest'.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Maybe something like lying in a hammock?
Maybe clearing your mind and thinking about nothing.
I'm afraid that would be a bit difficult.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Frima has been sleeping in the hammock since early this morning.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It'd be rude of me to wake her and wrestle it away from her.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Like meditation?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Close your eyes and focus on the sound of the sea.
Hmm... My mind does feel less cluttered now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Thanks, Subordinate.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I take some time to have a proper rest.
I bought a pearl necklace from Yan today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I initially wasn't sold on it,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: but Yan kept saying how this necklace would be perfect for me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: She said it looks great on me, so...
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I think it suits you well.
Another victim of her peerless salesmanship.
You think so?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I thought I'd fallen for her old sales tricks.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Well, I suppose I can wear this the next time there's a party on the ship.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I know...
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You think if I return it, she'd give me a refund?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I talk more about the pearl necklace.
You don't look well, Subordinate.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Are you all right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I might have a mild bout of heatstroke.
I was out of sorts, but now that you're here, I feel energized.
It's easy to get overheated in this weather.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Do you want to lie on my lap for a while?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: If you don't feel better after resting for a bit, I'll take you to see Mary.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: If you can still joke around like that, I'd say you're doing just fine.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Although it wouldn't hurt for you to go see Mary.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm takes me to visit Mary.
The stars tonight seem extra bright.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Is it true that your wishes will come true if you wish upon a star?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: If it is, what wish would you make, Subordinate?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: That we can one day reclaim the surface.
That I'll win the lottery.
We have the same wish.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I want to reclaim the surface as soon as possible
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: and explore the sea there.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: If I were to win the lottery,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: we probably wouldn't need to drum up donations anymore.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I wouldn't have to kiss up to potential sponsors either.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: ... But this whole thing with shooting stars is just a fantasy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I watch the stars together and make wishes.
Finally, I can swim to my heart's content.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Are you a good swimmer, Subordinate?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I can't even doggy paddle.
I could swim laps around you.
How about I give you some lessons?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: It's a good idea to at least learn the basics.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: How about we go for a swim after this session?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: You've got me feeling competitive again.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: After our session is over, I go swimming with Helm.
Anis threw a starfish at me today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I thought I was done with that while we're here.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'll give it up to her though, her aim is impressive.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I got plastered with one as well.
Are you okay?
You too?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Pfft.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'm imagining you two hurling starfish at each other.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I have to thank you for providing me with such a funny image.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'm fine.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Anchor has been giving me some training on how to dodge starfish.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I should be able to evade it next time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I talk more about starfish.
Mast told me I should take more pictures.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: But what should I photograph?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Me.
The ocean.
Why you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: If anything, I think Mast was referring to the ocean.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Mast will love that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I can also get some photos of birds that look like Morgan.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: And starfish that Anchor likes so much.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: And...
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I take a plethora of photos together.
Anis and I agreed to have a two-on-two water fight.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Would you like to join us?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Sure. I'll be on your team.
Sure. I'll be on Anis' team.
I'll do everything I can to make sure you win.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Wait, no, so that we win, I mean...
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I think Anis is going to team up with Neon.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: But if you really want to be on her side,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I'll team up with Neon.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: ... I guess I'll go inform Anis.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I have a good time having a water fight.
Subordinate, is there any nickname you'd like me to call you by?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Since we're at the beach,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I thought it might be better to use a new nickname.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: {AccountData.NickName}?
I like Subordinate just fine.
Huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Now that I think of it, I've never called you by your actual name.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Okay, for today, that's what I'll call you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: ... If you say so.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Feels like kind of a waste though...
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Helm and I continue discussing the notion of nicknames.
... Subordinate.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Is there something on my face?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Why do you keep staring at me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Because you're gorgeous.
Because you look so powerful when you're by the sea.
You're incorrigible.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I already told you before,
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: don't look at me like that unless you really mean it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: Thank you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: That's the first time anyone has ever said that to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Helm

adviseScripts.text: I spend a meaningful session with Helm.
